    "threads: ordered reading sequences. Each member gets prev/next links.",
    "  This is what makes the graph navigable instead of a hairball: a cluster",
    "  of N posts gets N-1 edges, not N*(N-1)/2.",
    "bridges: conceptual links ACROSS threads, bidirectional. These are the",
